## Recommendation

**Keep Both:**
- Use [wallet_client.py](file:///c:/Users/rovie%20segubre/agent/wallet_client.py) as your **infrastructure layer** (for building agents)
- Use [smart_wallet.py](file:///c:/Users/rovie%20segubre/agent/smart_wallet.py) as your **user interface** (for manual testing)

This separation follows the Unix philosophy: build composable tools that do one thing well.
